Comment: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊...
Comment: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可別怪我了...
Comment: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬可...
