Comment: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,同伴在我面前被吃掉了
Comment: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明同伴被吃掉了...
