Comment: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是...
Comment: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打從心底覺得「好險不是我」
Comment: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過...
Comment: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來就輪到我了
Comment: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我終於發現了
Comment: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們的工作就是...
