Comment: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,與其被吃掉還不如...
Comment: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手 振作一點!
Comment: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又不只是你
Comment: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家都在與恐懼奮鬥著
Comment: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你看看莎夏!
Comment: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是遇上那種事 依然是個驕傲的士兵
Comment: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的肚子好痛...
