Comment: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼只有一發?
Comment: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,煙在...
